caption:
#Pixel9a is AI magic made simple.

📷 Snap awe-worthy moments on the best-in-class camera that lets you work wonders
💪 Handle dust, dings, and drops with our most durable A-series phone yet¹
🔍 Ask @googlegemini to find info and complete tasks across your Google apps²
🔋 Leave the charger at home with over 30+ hours of battery life—that's nearly 25% longer than #Pixel8a³

More than you expect, for less than you think. Magic is at your fingertips with Pixel 9a at GoogleStore.com 

¹Designed to comply with dust and water protection rating IP68 under IEC standard 60529 when each device leaves the factory but the device is not water or dust proof. The accessories are not water or dust resistant. Water resistance and dust resistance are not permanent conditions and will diminish or be lost over time due to normal wear and tear, device repair, disassembly or damage. Phone is not drop/tumble proof and dropping your device may result in loss of water/dust resistance. Damage from drops, tumbles, and other external forces is not covered under warranty. Liquid damage voids the warranty. See g.co/pixel/water for details.
²Gemini mobile app available on select devices, languages, and countries. Internet connection required. Check responses for accuracy. 
³Compared to Pixel 8a. Average reflected and based on testing using a median Pixel user battery usage profile across a mix of talk, data, standby, and use of other features. Battery testing conducted on a major US carrier network in California in late 2024 on pre-production hardware and software using default settings. Tests began with phones fully charged. Actual battery life may be lower. Battery life improvement based on internal data using pre-production devices. Battery life and improvement depends upon many factors. Usage of certain features will decrease battery life. Actual improvement percentage may vary. Over time, Pixel software will manage battery performance to help maintain battery health as your battery ages. See g.co/pixel/batteryhealth for details.
